<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يَا أَخِي <span class="c2">(أَصْلَحَكَ الله)</span> هَذَا عَمَلٌ غَيرُ صَالحْ ٠٠!!<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">بِالرَّدِّ عَلَى الهَدَايَا:</span> دَخَلنَا مَعَاً مُسَابَقَةً فَفَازُواْ وَخَسِرْت؛ فَبَعَثُواْ لِي بِهَدِيَّةٍ يُوَاسُونَني بِهَا،<span class="c5"> فَبَعَثتُ إِلَيْهِمْ بهَذِهِ الآيَة:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(*)</span> <span class="c2">(أَتمِدُّونَني بمَالٍ فَمَا آتَانِيَ اللهُ خَيْرٌ ممَّا آتَاكُمْ، بَلْ أَنْتُمْ بِهَدِيَّتِكُمْ تَفرَحُون)</span> <span class="c2">(*)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(*)</span> <span class="c2">(طَوَارِئُ مُبَوَّبَة)</span> <span class="c2">(*)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">الحُمَاقَة ــ بِالأَجِنْدَةِ الخَضْرَاء:</span> أَلَيْسَ مِتكُمْ رَجُلٌ رَشِيدْ ٠٠!؟<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">بِالمَأكُولاَتِ وَالمَشْرُوبَاتْ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ـ <span class="c2">(طَلَبْ سَحْلَبْ)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>ـ السَّحْلَبْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ـ السَّحْلَبْ فَاتْ فَاتْ فَاتْ وِفي ذيلُه سَبَعْ لَفَّاتْ ٠٠!!<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">عَلَى ثَلاَجَة مَاء صَدَقَةً جَارِيَةً يَشْرَبُ مِنهَا السَّابِلَة:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c1">" عَيْنَاً يَشْرَبُ بِهَا عِبَادُ اللهِ يُفَجِّرُونَهَا تَفجِيرَا "</span> ٠٠!!<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">بِالحِرَفْ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>